{520}{}{他们只有一个水源。如果我们毒死它。。。 -- They have just one source of water. If we poison it...}
#{521}{}{Not yet, but if you bring me to their camp, I'm sure I can think of something.}
{521}{}{还没有，但如果你带我去他们的营地，我肯定能想到点什么。 -- Not yet, but if you bring me to their camp, I'm sure I can think of something.}
#{522}{}{No, not yet.}
{522}{}{不，还没有。 -- No, not yet.}
#{523}{}{This is cunning, outsider. But you will have to go elsewhere to find this poison. We have nothing like that here.}
