{536}{}{现在不行。我待会儿再跟你谈。 -- Not right now. I'll talk to you later.}
#{540}{}{More children of the Devourer will come. We will break the cycle before it begins again. These lands have fed the Cheyenne for many years, but now it is time to leave them.}
{540}{}{更多的吞食者的孩子会来。我们将在循环重新开始之前打破它。这些土地养活了夏延人很多年，但现在是时候离开他们了。 -- More children of the Devourer will come. We will break the cycle before it begins again. These lands have fed the Cheyenne for many years, but now it is time to leave them.}
#{541}{}{You're leaving? Why didn't you just do that before?}
{541}{}{你要走了？你以前为什么不这么做？ -- You're leaving? Why didn't you just do that before?}
