#{550}{}{[He sighs] Only Heavenly Mother knows.}
{550}{}{只有天母知道。 -- [He sighs] Only Heavenly Mother knows.}
#{551}{}{If I can operate on him before you leave, he might just make it. But I need your permission, first.}
