{1570}{}{这开启了夏延人的新纪元！我们将永远记住你，你是一只雷霆鸟！请拿着这个护身符。当你穿着它的时候，请记住我们的人民，愿它永远照亮你的道路。 -- This begins a new era for the Cheyenne! We will remember you always as Bensy - Thunder Bird! Please, take this amulet. Remember our people when you wear it, and may it bring light to your path forever.}
